                                <ns0:support>
                                    <ns0:p>A rectangular tablet of fine white marble, with a break down the middle and minor chipping to the edges. The rear is lightly convex, and smooth; the remains of a border along the upper rear face suggest the tablet has been re-used for the inscription.</ns0:p>
                                        <ns0:material ana="#material.stone.marble" ref="http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/48.html">marble</ns0:material>
