                        </ns0:objectDesc>
                        <ns0:handDesc>
                            <ns0:handNote><ns0:p>Lunate Greek letters, neatly and regularly engraved, with only lightly pronounced terminal serifs. Alpha has an upward-sloping cross-bar. Beta is closed with almost equal eyes. Delta and Lambda extend the right hasta above the letter. Theta and Omicron are ovoid in form. Mu generally has vertical first and last strokes,with the middle-point only descending half-way.</ns0:p>
